odone, Methadone, Pentazocine, Buprenorphine, Oliceridine, Morphine, Butorphanol, Fentanyl, Codeine, More', 'Entrectinib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Pacritinib, Tepotinib, Fedratinib, Avapritinib, Larotrectinib, Bosutinib, Vemurafenib, Lapatinib, More', 1767369485);
